text: The Mindanao rasbora (Rasbora philippina) is a rasbora native to Mindanao, Philippines. It is listed as Near Threatened. == References == # Froese, Rainer; Pauly, Daniel (eds.) (2013). "Rasbora philippina" in FishBase. April 2013 version. Category:IUCN Red List near threatened species Category:Philippines Category:Ray-finned fish Category:Cypriniformes
title: Mindanao rasbora
